GG_CASTLE_WARS

***************


(Special thanks to Hamster for the textures)

This map is all about fun. It was made over the course of 2-3 days and only has about 20 hours of work. I used Hamster's custom textures to make it. You can find his FPSB profile here:

http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/153451


MAP FEATURES:

** Ultra-fast routes to each side of the map on the outward sides!
** Breakable bricks that line the top perimeter of each castle!
** Breakable crates all over the outside of the map!
** Strategically placed HE Grenades!


NOTES:

I really wanted to make a Simpsons map. If anyone wants to let me borrow their Simpsons textures I would appreciate it.


COME PLAY THIS MAP ON MY SERVER:

72.26.102.140:27015


Please leave questions/comments/suggestions. Also, did I mention I want some Simpsons textures? :)


ENJOY !!!
